  "description": "Tools to download global and European geospatial data from Eurostat's GISCO (Geographic Information System of the Commission) database <https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/web/gisco>. The package provides helpers for working with country boundaries, NUTS regions, statistical units, transport networks and other geospatial datasets. This package is not officially related to or endorsed by Eurostat.",
